		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://www.anomalycon.com/anomalycon-2015/new-hotel/" rel="bookmark">New Hotel!</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Due to management changes at the DTC Marriott and feedback we&#8217;ve received from attendees, we have made the decision to change venues to the DTC Hyatt. Rooms are now available for reservation for <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">$89/night</span> $90/night, and you can reserve under the AnomalyCon reservation rate for Thu, Fri, Sat and Sun nights. Click HERE<a href="https://resweb.passkey.com/go/Anomalycon2015"></a> or visit our location page to make your reservation while rooms are available!</p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
